column5:
Fixed FF bugs by removing alpha:false from the context creation;
Fixed mesh particle related bugs;
Removed ANGLE check;
Added emitterRadius;
Added docs for new properties;
Removed nasty branching from the particle updater shader;

Name changes:
spawnBounds -> emitterExtents
spawnShape -> emitterShape
pc.PARTICLESHAPE -> pc.EMITTERSHAPE

Fixed repetition of random;
Fixed spherical emission;
Added DX9 check and temporary fallback to CPU;
Fixed mesh particles.

Normal offset shadow bias;
Fixed bugs with point shadows;
emissiveIntensity;
heightMapMultiplier;
Shader optimizations.

Particle fixes.

Fixed alignToMotion;
Added check for more than 65k verts in particle system;
Fixed gamma correction on particles in some conditions;
Fixed particle shader caching key generation;
Fixed runtime CPU-GPU particle switch;
Fixed sorting of mesh particles;
wrapBounds are now relative to emitter pos instead of camera pos;
mode parameter now uses enum, not string;
Fixed mobile particle problems;
Depth softening control is now a bit more intuitive;
Added _activeCamera to scene object (actually last rendered camera);
Fixed depth softening bugs;
Removed camera property from particle system.

New particle interface and underlying logic:
- reset() resets particle state, doesn't affect playing;
- stop() disables the emission of new particles;
- play() continues the emission, also unpauses;
- pause() freezes the emitter;
- isPlaying() tells if emission is in progress;
- "oneShot" parameter replaced with "loop" (same, but inversed);
- non-looped emitters do not start emission unless play() is called;

simple and sparks examples are updated.

Fixed CPU stretching.
Fixed WebGL warning spamming by disallowing particles being rendered into depth map. Added meshInstance.drawToDepth boolean to control it.

- Fixed light intensity issues;
- Added scene-wide prefilteredCubeMap properties;
- Shader now uses scene's prefilteredCubeMap if it's not overridden in material;
- Removed forgotten console.log;
- Added temporary workaround code for loading prefilteredCubeMaps from static address.

- Fixed fog not blending correctly;
- Moved fog to shaderChunks;
- Fixed caching key generation for all material shaders (source of multiple bugs, like shaders not updating when changing fog at runtime).

Fixed appearance of different blends, removed premultiplied blend from particles;
Fixed lifetime change weirdness, removed lifetime2;
Fixed alpha2 not working in CPU mode;
Fixed preWarm;
Fixed bug with color intensity multiplying alpha;
Particle gamma correction is now off when no lighting is enabled on particles;
Fixed possible error on dynamic 'lighting' parameter change;
Fixed system disappearing after changing oneShot a few times;
Fixed endTime calculation for oneShot emitters (didn't take rate2 into account).

Point light shadows. There could be some problems on Intel videocards (?) and old Macs (?);
Falloff mode as light property;
Inverse squared falloff mode.

velocityGraph, localVelocityGraph, rotationSpeedGraph
Scale affects emitter;
Fixed oneShot resetting time and being complex parameter;
Changing graph properties doesn't require full rebuild;
spawnBounds now grow from center and not corner;
spawnBounds now rotate with entity;

Replaced Function.extendsFrom with pc.inherits()
Removed extendsFrom from the built-in Function object.
Replace this
Derived = Derived.extendsFrom(Base);
with this:
Derived = pc.inherits(Derived, Base);
